ACZ DISTRIBUTION Nevada, USA
Terms & Sales Agreement
By signing below, Applicant herby agrees to the following terms and conditions of sale.
1. Applicant shall pay for all items purchased and services rendered in accordance with the terms and conditions established by ACZ Distribution. Absent any written agreement to the contrary signed by both Applicant and ACZ Distribution, payments for all purchases are due within 48 hours after receipt of reimbursement from payers is collected.
2. All payments shall be made in form satisfactory to ACZ Distribution. Applicant shall pay a late payment charge of 1.5% or the maximum rate permitted by law, assessed monthly until paid in full on any amount not paid when due. Applicant shall also pay all losses, costs, attorney's fees or other expenses incurred by ACZ Distribution as a result of Applicant's failure to comply with the terms of this agreement. Failure or delay by ACZ Distribution to bill for any such late payment or other charge or expense shall not waive or otherwise affect ACZ Distributions right to collect these charges.
3. ACZ Distribution, reserves the right at all times to limit or terminate the extension of credit and to modify its terms of sale.
4. Applicant acknowledges they are responsible for any and all material once sealed packages are opened regardless of use. They may also be responsible for unused product if it is not returned in a timely and appropriate manner as requested by distributor.
5. Applicant must show ACZ an EOB when asked. If applicant can not provide EOB, they must provide documentation showing they have not received reimbursement. EX. appeal process, denial of reimbursement, etc. Anticipated Average Monthly Volume
Applicant represents and warrants that all information provided in this Application or otherwise submitted is true and correct and is being furnished for the purpose of obtaining/retaining credit from ACZ Distribution.
